1. *Vrha* čaše je bio polomljen. (The *top* of the glass was broken.)
2. Ne mogu da se setim *vrha* svog jezika. (I can't remember the *tip* of my tongue.)
3. Umetnik je pažljivo držao četkicu na *vrhu* prstiju. (The artist carefully held the brush on the *tip* of his fingers.)
4. *Vrh* planine bio je prekriven snegom. (The *summit* of the mountain was covered in snow.)
5. Njegova kompanija je dostigla *vrh* poslovne piramide. (His company reached the *top* of the business pyramid.)
6. Čekao je da se vrata lifta otvore na *vrhu* zgrade. (He waited for the elevator doors to open at the *top* of the building.)
7. Kao dete, voleo je da vidi *vrhove* drveća. (As a child, he liked to see the *tops* of trees.)
8. Profesor je *vrh* u svom polju istraživanja. (The professor is a *top* in his field of research.)
9. *Vrhunac* njegovog nastupa bio je zadivljujući solo na gitari. (The *climax* of his performance was a stunning guitar solo.)
10. Njegov tim je uspešno savladao sve prepreke na putu do *vrhunca* takmičenja. (His team successfully overcame all obstacles on the way to the *peak* of the competition.)